Hi Bob,

Jamie Rivers carries his "Blue Sky" tarp poles this way on the drivers 
side of his 74 westy. It keeps them outside the vehicle and the center 
of gravity is nice and low for better handling. You can see the poles 
enroute to EveryBus 2002 in this pic:

http://pottsfamily.ca/VW_type2/EB2002/AGF00113.JPG

Happy trails,

Greg Potts
Toronto, Ontario, Canada

